<TITLE> Schools, colleges closed from Sept 16 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Sept 12 (bdnews24.com)  All schools including English-medium ones, colleges and madrasas in the city will remain closed from Sept 16 to the end of the government holidays for Eid-ul-Fitr. The education ministry on Thursday announced the closure of the institutions and asked all to comply with the directive. bd
